Sin - Class in plugins
This tool creates a new raster in which each grid cell is equal to the sine of the corresponding grid cell in an input raster.
Sin() - Constructor for class plugins.Sin
 
Sinh - Class in plugins
This tool creates a new raster in which each grid cell is equal to the hyperbolic sine of the corresponding grid cell in an input raster.
Sinh() - Constructor for class plugins.Sinh
 
SqrRt - Class in plugins
This tool creates a new raster in which each grid cell is equal to the square root of the value of the corresponding grid cell in the input raster.
SqrRt() - Constructor for class plugins.SqrRt
 
Square - Class in plugins
This tool creates a new raster in which each grid cell is equal to the square of the value of the corresponding grid cell in the input raster
Square() - Constructor for class plugins.Square
 
Subtract - Class in plugins
This tool creates a new raster in which each grid cell is equal to the subtraction of the corresponding grid cells in two input rasters or one input raster and a constant value.
Subtract() - Constructor for class plugins.Subtract
